  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.7">
<l>uḷḷu ḷāvi yularntularnteṉa</l>
<l>vaḷḷalē kaṇṇaṉē yeṉṉumpiṉṉum</l>
<l>veḷḷanīrk kiṭantā yeṉṉumeṉ</l>
<l>kaḷvitāṉ paṭṭa vañcaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Inside, inside her soul is all dried up” –</l>
<l>“o liberal man, o Kaṇṇaṉ”, she says, [then] again</l>
<l>“o you who lied on the water of the flood”, she says.</l>
<l>O you deceiver that my secretive [girl] has fallen for.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
